#- Welcome to the§0
§0Nexus Brewer's Guide!§0
§0In these pages we  will teach you how§0
§0to impress your§0
§0friends, amaze your colleagues, and get your enemies drunk as a skunk!§0
§0( Only guarateed to impress or amaze if they're impressed or amazed by booze )
#- ===================§0
§0           Index§0
§0===================§0
§0
§0Getting Started----§f.§06§0
§0-Fermenting-------6§0
§0-Distilling---------§f.§09§0
§0-Aging-----------11§0
§0
§0Recipes----------21§0
§0-Potato Soup-----§f.§022§0
